Aldehyde dehydrogenase (EC 1.2.1.3).
"Expression of the Vibrio cholerae gene encoding aldehyde
dehydrogenase is under control of ToxR, the cholera toxin
transcriptional activator.";
"A Vibrio cholerae pathogenicity island associated with epidemic and
pandemic strains.";
"Comparison of Vibrio cholerae pathogenicity islands in sixth and
