-!- FUNCTION: May be involved in V.cholerae virulence, as its
    expression is under the control of toxR, a transcriptional
    activator of several genes associated with virulence.
-!- CATALYTIC ACTIVITY: An aldehyde + NAD(+) + H(2)O = an acid + NADH.
-!- PATHWAY: Ethanol utilization; second step.
-!- SIMILARITY: Belongs to the aldehyde dehydrogenase family.
